    "1400708": {
        "Desc": "Review official documents",
        "Step": "Neuvillette is focused on reviewing the official documents. Help him find points of suspicion",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Charlotte",
                    "T": "Strange... Why isn't he back yet..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Gotcha!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Charlotte",
                    "T": "Whoa!!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Charlotte!? What are you doing here?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wait, don't tell Paimon you're the one who sent Kiara that threatening letter! But you don't seem like the type toâ€”"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Charlotte",
                    "T": "Threat letter? What threat letter?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What are you doing here, exactly?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Charlotte",
                    "T": "Uh, this is starting to feel like an interrogation... Okay, I'll be straight with you. I don't know the slightest thing about that threat letter you mentioned â€” I only wanted to follow Monsieur Neuvillette and request an interview with him."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "You wanna interview him?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Charlotte",
                    "T": "That's right! I'm not the only one, y'know. Interviewing him is every journalist's dream."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Charlotte",
                    "T": "But it's not an easy task to accomplish. The Palais Mermonia rarely accepts appointment requests from us, and we never have the chance to interrupt when the court's in session."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Charlotte",
                    "T": "So imagine how surprised I was seeing him out on the streets today! It seemed like you were investigating something too... The perfect opportunity to whip up an exclusive, don't you think?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Charlotte",
                    "T": "Of course, I'll make sure to turn in my manuscript to him for review. I have my principles, and I'd never publish an article without the consent of all parties involved."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I don't think he'd agree..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It's better if we kept this secret."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yeah! We're doing a secret investigation that can't be made public knowledge!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Charlotte",
                    "T": "I see... Well, if you say so, I guess I'll put this matter aside for now. What a shame... Chances like this don't come by very often, you know."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Charlotte",
                    "T": "In exchange, could you tell me what the threat letter is about? I swear I won't tell!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Alright then..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "You tell Charlotte about the letter Kiara received..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Charlotte",
                    "T": "WHAT!? Someone's targeting a cute little Melusine?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Shh, not so loud!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Charlotte",
                    "T": "It just so happens that I did an interview with Kiara â€” last month, in fact. It was well-received by our readers, so I was planning to continue the series... and now someone's coming after her?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Charlotte",
                    "T": "I'll ask my colleagues about it. Who knows? We might find something. And don't worry, I know what I'm doing! This secret's safe with me."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Charlotte",
                    "T": "But I gotta warn you, even if I keep my lips sealed, others will know eventually."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Why?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Charlotte",
                    "T": "People care a great deal about Monsieur Neuvillette's each and every move. Some may have already realized that something was up. Besides, the case involves Melusines, so..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Charlotte",
                    "T": "Anyway, I'll get going now. Watch yourselves, alright?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Well, that was a nice chat... Let's head back and check on Kiara."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
