    "1400901": {
        "Desc": "Go to the Fortress of Meropide",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "Welcome to the Fortress of Meropide, dear esteemed guests."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "We're back!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ooh, and a greeting from none other than the Duke himself! Guess we've made a name for ourselves at this place, hehe."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "This isn't anything new. I figured you had important matters to discuss when the two of you â€” not to mention the Chief Justice â€” showed up."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "Let us assume we've gone through the pleasantries and cut right to the chase."
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "You tell Wriothesley about the threat letter Kiara received..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "I do remember a thing or two about Domenico. He once attempted to round up the other inmates and instigate a protest."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Who does this guy think he is!? Paimon hopes nothing came of it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "He \"once attempted to,\" I said, meaning that it was over before it even started. And now he's threatening Melusines, is he?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "...To be honest, Domenico doesn't seem like much of a conspirator. The fact that the three of you bothered to personally investigate raises a flag... Is there something else going on behind the scenes here?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh, he's got the same concerns we do!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Neuvillette",
                    "T": "I am concerned about this incident because something similar has occurred in the past. I wish to meet Domenico in person and have my questions answered."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "That's an easy one. Let me think, I think he's at..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sigewinne",
                    "T": "Did I hear someone say \"Melusine\"? What happened?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Sigewinne!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "A Melusine named Kiara received a threatening letter."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yeah, and we're investigating! The person who threatened her seems to be held imprisoned here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sigewinne",
                    "T": "Really? Is Kiara gonna be okay?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Neuvillette",
                    "T": "There's no need to worry. Clorinde is protecting her as we speak."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sigewinne",
                    "T": "Oh, that's great. But if the criminal's still... Is there anything you can do about this?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "Ah, Head Nurse, do you require me to personally deal with the criminal?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Neuvillette",
                    "T": "Wriothesley."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "Okay, I get it. I'll bring Domenico to you â€” that's your only demand, correct?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Neuvillette",
                    "T": "Think of it as more of a humble request. I am here on my own accord, not to formally transfer a criminal for trial. I urge you to set aside any concerns."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Neuvillette",
                    "T": "Thanks for the trouble. Consider me in your debt."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Whoa... If Paimon were you, Your Grace, Paimon would take this chance to ask for something really important!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "Well, were I still a criminal, I'd probably ask for a lighter sentence â€” but I'm sure Monsieur Neuvillette would reject that."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "But enough jokes. I'll look for Domenico and bring him to you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "Make yourselves at home. Our dear Head Nurse has mentioned you quite a few times, so I'm sure she has a lot to say."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
